# Salers AI

**AI sales coach that boosts rep performance and automates the busywork.**

Salers AI is a sales enablement platform that provides real-time coaching during calls, automated follow-up, and a lightweight CRM hub. By analyzing meetings, pipeline data, and activity patterns, Salers AI tells reps who to contact next, what to say, and removes repetitive admin tasks. It integrates with Zoom and Google to help small sales teams sell like top performers without the complexity or overhead of enterprise tools.

## Core Capabilities
- Real-time coaching prompts during live sales calls
- Automated follow-up emails and task reminders
- Lightweight CRM for contacts and deals
- Integrations: Zoom, Google Calendar, Gmail

